<div class="p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-xl shadow-md bp-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-center">
        BOYS AND GIRLS DORMITORY RULES
    </h1>

    <ol class="space-y-2 list-decimal list-inside">
        <li class="text-lg">Only <span class="font-bold">REGISTERED</span> students are allowed to occupy the dormitory and use the facilities provided.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Students must live in a room that has been designated by the Seremban TAFE College administration. Any room transfer is <span class="font-bold">not allowed without permission</span> from the Seremban TAFE College administration.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Smoking is <span class="font-bold">PROHIBITED</span> in the dormitory area and College area.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Rooms <span class="font-bold">must be vacated</span> during holidays or instructed by the TAFE SEREMBAN COLLEGE administration.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Students who want to leave the dormitory / return to the village should fill in the information on the <span class="font-bold">LEAVE FORM</span> provided at the Guard House.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">All students must be in the Dormitory Building <span class="font-bold">NO LATER THAN 10:00 PM</span>, unless due to unavoidable circumstances and with permission.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">It is not allowed to bring in outside guests to the dormitory room. All dormitory facilities must be used <span class="font-bold">CAREFULLY</span> and not intentionally do anything that can mutilate, stain or cause any damage.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Students who deliberately damage parts of the building and dormitory equipment will be asked to pay compensation and may also be subject to disciplinary action.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Dormitory students are not allowed to <span class="font-bold">enter other students' rooms without the permission</span> of the occupants.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">All dormitory students are responsible for the tidiness and cleanliness of their respective rooms, rubbish must be disposed of in the bins provided.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">All students are responsible if the items in their rooms are lost or damaged and must be reported to the <span class="font-bold">TAFE SEREMBAN COLLEGE administration immediately.</span></li>
        <li class="text-lg">Please make sure the room is locked every time you leave it.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Students are <span class="font-bold">not allowed to be in the dormitory</span> during learning hours.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">Everyone must ensure that the lights are <span class="font-bold">switched on at 12 o'clock at night.</span></li>
        <li class="text-lg">Use electricity and water facilities wisely. Don't <span class="font-bold">WASTE.</span></li>
        <li class="text-lg">It is forbidden to paste any poster or any type of paste that damages or stains the dormitory.</li>
        <li class="text-lg">It is forbidden to cook food inside the dormitory building.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="mt-4 font-bold text-red-600">
        STRICT ACTION WILL BE TAKEN ON DORMEROUS RESIDENTS WHO VIOLATE THE SET DORMEROUSRULES RULES.
    </p>
</div>
